00:04:36.612 --> 00:04:40.180
Now before I write down
all of Newton's laws,

00:04:40.180 --> 00:04:44.540
I'll just write down our
various force diagrams.

00:04:44.540 --> 00:04:50.300
So for pulley A,
I have two strings

00:04:50.300 --> 00:04:52.370
