00:08:12.400 --> 00:08:17.880
Now if you think about what
I said before about combining

00:08:17.880 --> 00:08:22.610
systems, if we combine
pulley B in block 2,

00:08:22.610 --> 00:08:25.420
visually what we're doing
is we're just adding these

00:08:25.420 --> 00:08:27.640
to free body diagram together.

00:08:27.640 --> 00:08:33.400
When we have a
system B and block 2.

00:08:33.400 --> 00:08:36.640
